{"name":"Scion Tolus","size":"medium","type":"celestial","tag":"Grand Council, Gilean","alignment":"Neutral Good","hitDice":"15","armorName":"half plate","shieldBonus":2,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"10","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"22 (5d8)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"8","dexPoints":"14","conPoints":"14","intPoints":"18","wisPoints":"20","chaPoints":"10","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"7","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Channel Divinity: Knowledge of the Ages","desc":"[MON] reaches out to his god and receives an answer to any questions he may have, regardless of how ancient, forbidden, forgotten, or esoteric the knowledge is."},{"name":"Forbidden Knowledge","desc":"[MON] is immune to all the harmful effects of Forbidden Knowledge. Other creatures that learn about this information are inflicted with long-term madness."},{"name":"Spellcasting","desc":"[MON] is a spellcaster (spell save DC [WIS SAVE], [WIS ATK] to hit).\n\n> Cantrips (at will): _Guidance, Light, Toll the Dead, Sacred Flame_\n> 1st level (4 slots): _Identify, Healing Word, Detect Evil and Good, Guiding Bolt_\n> 2nd level (4 slots): _Augury, Detect Thoughts, Zone of Truth, Hold Person, Spiritual Weapon_\n> 3rd level (2 slots): _Spirit Guardians, Dispel Magic, Daylight_\n> 4th level (1 slot): _Divination_"}],"actions":[{"name":"Celestial Revelation","desc":"[MON] transforms into an Aasimar and gains 30ft. of flight speed."},{"name":"Divine Aid","desc":"If [MON] uses the help action, the targeted creature rolls 3 dice (instead of 2) and takes the highest one."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"wis","order":4},{"name":"cha","order":5}],"skills":[{"name":"arcana","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"insight","stat":"wis","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"investigation","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"medicine","stat":"wis"},{"name":"nature","stat":"int"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"religion","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"survival","stat":"wis"}],"damagetypes":[{"name":"necrotic","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"radiant","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"All","speaks":false}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Scion","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}